SKAM France Renewal Celebration: Wednesday: 

Plotline Speculations for S5

 

What issues would you like to see tackled ? I...
caption:
SKAM France Renewal Celebration:

Wednesday:  Plotline Speculations for S5

What issues would you like to see tackled ? I would like to know if the famous Tuturo874 is a coincidence or it has something to do with his ig account? i would like to see more about his what it’s seem like to be drug addiction and that could be leading to overdose or big problem with drug dealer or justice. To know what’s the deal about that 34year old woman, did say that to brag to the boys or was he serious? And as his season will air during his Bac year and the year that you are supposed to chose your future life i would like to see him struggle with class and stress that could be coming from his home life too. Him having very strict parents who could always be behind his back, always pushing him to do what they want and not what he want to do and that could be leading to him having abusive parents. Also i like the idea of him having sibling that would look up to him and that he could be in charge of and be super protective of.

The kid: can I have candy for dinner?

Eliott: what did Papa say?
